{"id":267268,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/奇闻录-让领导先走/","date":"2012-12-08T10:15:22Z","modified":"2014-12-18T22:38:47Z","title":"奇闻录 | 让领导先走","content":"<p>@李承鹏：18年前<a href=\"http://zh.wikipedia.org/zh/%E5%85%8B%E6%8B%89%E7%8E%9B%E4%BE%9D%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%AB\" rel=\"nofollow\">今天</a>，284名孩子被烧死在克拉玛依剧院。“让领导先走”阻止了他们逃生。有人否认，但两名幸存者证实现场确有领导说过这话。当时9岁的周雅静说：演出前我给他献花的那爷爷，用力推开我们向前跑。“让领导先走”已成中国官员一切领域最卑鄙也最当然的通行证。改变“让领导先走”，中国才不会倒退。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/12/Screen-shot-2012-12-08-at-11.40.15-AM.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-267270\" title=\"Screen shot 2012-12-08 at 11.40.15 AM\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/12/Screen-shot-2012-12-08-at-11.40.15-AM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"495\" height=\"362\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/12/Screen-shot-2012-12-08-at-11.40.15-AM.png 495w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/12/Screen-shot-2012-12-08-at-11.40.15-AM-300x219.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 495px) 100vw, 495px\" /></a></p>\n<p>@大尸凶的漫画：《幸存者》卡拉玛依大火十八周年纪念。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/767e4963tw1dzmczm02whj.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/767e4963tw1dzmczm02whj.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" /></a></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=N1Dd3YCw0pQ:3Sr6a-1rHn8:yIl2AUoC8zA\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=N1Dd3YCw0pQ:3Sr6a-1rHn8:7Q72WNTAKBA\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=N1Dd3YCw0pQ:3Sr6a-1rHn8:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?i=N1Dd3YCw0pQ:3Sr6a-1rHn8:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/q